{"lemma":"شَكِّ","slug":"شَكِّ","root":"ش.ك.ك","root_slug":"ش-ك-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ك-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَكّ","root":"شكك","pos":"N","occurrence_count":15},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":14},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22783","n22785","n22786"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%90%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to doubt, be doubtful, suspect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be scandalized"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause doubts or scruples"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to scandalize"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pierce with a lance to the bones, pierce through"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lean upon, lean against"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stick together, clump together, adhere, cohere"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to halt, limp"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to arm oneself from head to foot"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to build the houses in one row"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَكَّ (šakka, “to doubt”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"doubt, uncertainty, suspicion, scruple, scandal, hesitation","examples":[{"text":"لَا شَكَّ","english":"there is no doubt"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"small tear (something torn), small rent, small split","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"white arsenic, arsenic trioxide","tags":["obsolete"],"examples":[{"text":"شك: هو التراب الهالك عند أهل العراق وهو سم الفار أيضاً، وعند أهل المغرب هو رهج الفار. وقال الرازي في خواصه: الشك شيء يؤتى به من بلاد خراسان من معادن الفضة وهو نوعان أبيض وأصفر إن جعل في عجين وطرح في بيت فأكل منه الفار مات ومات كل فارة تشم ريح ذلك الفار حتى يموت الكل أجمع وهو صحيح وقد وقفت عليه. الرازي في المنصوري: الزنجفر والشك يعرض من شربهما مثل ما يعرض من الزئبق المقتول إلا أن الشك أقوى جداً لأنه قاتل لا يتخلص منه وعلاجه مثل علاج من سقي الزئبق.","english":"De simplicibus medicinis opus magnum"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃakk/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22783","headword_ar":"شَكَّ","root":"$k","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is intrans. by itself, and trans. by means of the particle"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY","text_ar":"فى"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b2-  one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a AlA^amoru","text_ar":"شَكَّ الاَمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ya$uk~u","text_ar":"يَشُكُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[contr. to analogy in the case of an intrans. verb of this class], inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~N","text_ar":"شَكٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dubious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confused:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) ―         -b3-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a fiyhi","text_ar":"شَكَّ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, K,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akakotu fyh","text_ar":"شَكَكْتُ فيه"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) aor. as above, (JM, PS, &c.,) and so the inf. n., (MA, &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He doubted, wavered"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacillated in opinion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was uncertain, respecting it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, Msb, and so accord. to explanations of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~N","text_ar":"شَكٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. infrà] in the S and Msb and K &c.;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotaAba","text_ar":"اِرْتَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$k~k","text_ar":"تشكّك","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a EalaY~a","text_ar":"شَكَّ عَلَىَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amoru","text_ar":"الاَمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a","text_ar":"شَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, was difficult, hard, distressing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, TA:) or, as some say, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was such that"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I doubted"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akakotu","text_ar":"شَكَكْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"respecting it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a","text_ar":"شَكَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a camel, (IAar, S, K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He limped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"halted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had a slight lameness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his hind leg:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his arm stuck to his side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and he had a slight lameness in consequence thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$tk~","text_ar":"اشتكّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", likewise said of a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a slight lameness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, TA;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a","text_ar":"شَكَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn-'Abbád, O.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~N","text_ar":"شَكٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cleaving"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sticking"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of a thing to another thing]. (S, O, TA.) So in a verse of Aboo-Dahbal El-Jumahee cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yalabN","text_ar":"يَلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~ati Alr~aHimu","text_ar":"شَكَّتِ الرَّحِمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The relationship was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, closely united."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHimN $aAk~apN","text_ar":"رَحِمٌ شَاكَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAk~N","text_ar":"شَاكٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a fiY Als~ilaAHi","text_ar":"شَكَّ فِى السِّلَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put on"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attired himself with, the arms,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons, completely, not leaving any of them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he entered amid them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akakotuhu biAlr~umoHi","text_ar":"شَكَكْتُهُ بِالرُّمْحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, in the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~ahu","text_ar":"شَكَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~ahomi","text_ar":"بِالسَّهْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the like, aor. as above, (TA,) and so the inf. n., (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I pierced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transpierced, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEanotuhu","text_ar":"طَعَنْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Msb, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xazaqotuhu","text_ar":"خَزَقْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", O, and in like manner in the TA, but in my copies of the S"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraqotuhu","text_ar":"خَرَقْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made a hole in him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and thus in one place in the TA, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotaZamotuhu","text_ar":"اِنْتَظَمْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S O, and in like manner in the K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the spear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the arrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (TA:) but IDrd says that, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~N","text_ar":"شَكٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the conjoining two things"},{"kind":"text","text":"with an arrow or a spear: (O, TA:) [thus,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$ak~a rijolahu maEa rikaAbihi","text_ar":"فَشَكَّ رِجْلَهُ مَعَ رِكَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he clave and transpierced his leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot, together with his stirrup."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akakotu A_ilayohi AlbilaAda","text_ar":"شَكَكْتُ اـِلَيْهِ البِلَادَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I traversed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crossed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut through, the countries,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"districts, to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uk~a Ealayih Alv~awobu","text_ar":"شُكَّ عَلَيِه الثَّوْبُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The garment was put"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawn"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"together upon him, and fastened with a thorn"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wooden pin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was let down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made to hang down, upon him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~uwA buyuwtahumo","text_ar":"شَكُّوا بُيُوتَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They placed their tents in one row,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"series,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one regular order,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b5-  Hence;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~uwA","text_ar":"شَكُّوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroHaAma","text_ar":"الاَرْحَامَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They made the relationships to be closely connected."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uk~a","text_ar":"شُكَّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asserted, to be connected with the lineage of another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akakotuhu","text_ar":"شَكَكْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of anything means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I drew and joined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjoined, it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[to another thing]. (Msb.) [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I infixed it"},{"kind":"text","text":"in, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrust it"},{"kind":"text","text":"into, another thing.] ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA $ak~a","text_ar":"مَا شَكَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kafiY xaliyluhaA","text_ar":"كَفِى خَلِيلُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or, more probably,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA $uk~a","text_ar":"ما شُكَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] a phrase in a verse of El-Farezdak,] in which it forms an apodosis,] means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA qaArana","text_ar":"مَا قَارَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., app.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its friend"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sword,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the spear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"both of which are meanings of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxaliyl","text_ar":"الخَلِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"would not be conjoined"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grasped"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with my hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~a","text_ar":"شَكَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~awoba","text_ar":"الثَّوْبَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the sewer)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made the stitch-holes far apart"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in sewing the garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) [Thus the verb has two contr. meanings.]       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akikotu A_ilayohi","text_ar":"شَكِكْتُ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akikotuhu","text_ar":"شَكِكْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn- 'Abbád, O, and so in the K accord. to the TA, as also in the TK, in the CK and in my MS. copy of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akakotuhu","text_ar":"شَكَكْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyh","text_ar":"اليه"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I inclined to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trusted to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relied upon, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, so as to be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become, easy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quiet, in mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaned, rested,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relied, upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakanotu","text_ar":"رَكَنْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn-'Abbád, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","MA","K","S","O","TA","IAar","T"]},{"entry_id":"n22785","headword_ar":"شَكٌّ","root":"$k","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[used as a subst.] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Doubt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb; [see 1;]) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqiynN","text_ar":"يَقِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, Msb, K;) by which explanation is meant"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wavering"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1583},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacillation in opinion between two things, whether they be equal"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in probability"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such that one of them outweighs"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the other;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as the expositors explain its meaning in the Kur x. 94,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncertainty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wavering"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacillation in opinion, between two inconsistent things, without making either of them to outweigh the other in the estimation of him who conceives the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ak~","text_ar":"شَكّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pausing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hesitation, between two extremes that are equal"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in probability"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without the mind's inclining to either of them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"when one of them is made to outweigh, without the other's being rejected, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zan~N","text_ar":"ظَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (KT:) accord. to Er-Rághib, it is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"alternation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confusedness, of two inconsistent things, in the judgment of a man, and their being equal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is sometimes because of there being two indications, equal in his judgment, of the two inconsistent things; or of there being no indication thereof: and sometimes it relates to the question whether a thing be, or be not; and sometimes, to the question of what kind it is; and sometimes, to some of its qualities; and sometimes, to the accident that is the cause of its being: it is a species of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahol","text_ar":"جَهْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but is more special than this; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhl","text_ar":"جهل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes the utter nonexistence of knowledge of the two inconsistent things; so that every"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$k~","text_ar":"شكّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhl","text_ar":"جهل"},{"kind":"text","text":", but every"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhl","text_ar":"جهل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$k~","text_ar":"شكّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) accord. to some, the primary meaning is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state of commotion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disturbance, of the heart and mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ukuwkN","text_ar":"شُكُوكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu Al$~aki","text_ar":"يَوْمُ الشَّكِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day of which one doubts whether it be the last of one month or the first of the next month:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and generally,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether it be the last of Shaabán or the first of Ramadán;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and to fast on this day is forbidden.]       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small crack in a bone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A seam,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"line of sewing, of a garment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SwH","text_ar":"صوح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  [And accord. to Freytag,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A coat of mail composed of narrow rings:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but he names no authority for this.]       -A3-  And ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Arsenic;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain medicament, that destroys rats; brought from Khurásán, from the mines of silver;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of two kinds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yellow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"now known by the name of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sam~u AlfaA^ori","text_ar":"سَمُّ الفَاْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ratsbane"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","KT","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22786","headword_ar":"شِكٌّ","root":"$k","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hul~ap","text_ar":"حُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is put upon the backs of the two curved extremities of the bow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so says ISd. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}